hopobject.body: I'll call back later national medical centre dha karachi To prepare the almonds, melt the butter in a small frying pan over a medium heat. When it just begins to bubble, add the almonds and stir, moving them constantly for 5 minutes until they begin to turn golden. Take off the heat and toss with the sugar and salt. Leave to cool for 5 minutes. Serve the apricots with a spoonful of custard and a sprinkling of almonds.
